(16862, 1, '2017-10-11 06:40:39', '2017-10-11 06:40:39', '[vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="50" padding_bottom="30" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="grid" text_align="left" css_animation=""][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Overview</strong></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" color="#fcb13c" width="40"][vc_column_text]Our comprehensive recruitment service is designed to help find the right candidate to join their team, using all of our industry experience[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="50" padding_bottom="30" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="grid" text_align="left" css_animation=""][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Permanent Staff</strong></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" color="#fcb13c" width="40"][vc_column_text]Our comprehensive permanent recruitment service is designed to help clients find the right candidate to join their team, using our experience. With dedicated account managers, and unrivalled insight into what you require, choose Karechoice as your permanent recruitment partner. We can recruit a wide range of personnel including -\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Registered Nurses</li>\r\n 	<li>Home Managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Unit Managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Registered Managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Directors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe pre-screen responses for your vacancy against the person specification we will have drawn up together, in addition to other checks you have asked us to complete.\r\n\r\nSuitable candidates are then put through further identification checks before we forward you relevant CV’s and profiles.\r\n\r\nWhen you have selected the candidates you wish to interview, we will arrange interviews on your behalf and deal with administration and negotiation throughout the employment offer.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="50" padding_bottom="30" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="grid" text_align="left" css_animation=""][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Temporary Staffing</strong></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" color="#fcb13c" width="40"][vc_column_text]Our temporary staffing service is designed for those organisations that require temporary nursing and care staff to cover planned or unplanned staff absences. Karechoicecan help with staffing shortfalls in busy periods, with long-term sick or maternity leave and help free up existing staff when opening new wards or units.\r\n\r\nOur temporary staffing service is based on the central objective of providingappropriately trained workers in a timely and cost effective manner, and of a quality consistent with a client’s own staff. It is based on the three principles of quality, service and value.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" css_animation=""][vc_column][action full_width="yes" content_in_grid="yes" type="normal" text_font_weight="" show_button="yes" button_size="big_large" button_target="_self" button_text="02086165652" button_text_color="#ffffff" button_hover_text_color="#ffffff" button_background_color="#fbb03c" button_hover_background_color="#303030" background_color="#999ca3" border_color="#ffffff"]\r\n<h1 style="color: #fff;">Speak to us for more information</h1>\r\n[/action][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Healthcare Staffing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16767-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-10-11 06:40:39', '2017-10-11 06:40:39', '', 16767, 'http://pheonixtechnology.com/Healthcare/2017/10/11/16767-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
