(16864, 1, '2017-10-11 06:41:39', '2017-10-11 06:41:39', '[vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="50" padding_bottom="30" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="grid" text_align="left" css_animation=""][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Overview</strong></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" color="#fcb13c" width="40"][vc_column_text]Our comprehensive recruitment service is designed to help find the right candidate to join their team, using all of our industry experience[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="16863" img_size="full" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="full_width" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="50" padding_bottom="30" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="grid" text_align="left" css_animation=""][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><strong>Permanent Staff</strong></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" color="#fcb13c" width="40"][vc_column_text]Our comprehensive permanent recruitment service is designed to help clients find the right candidate to join their team, using our experience. With dedicated account managers, and unrivalled insight into what you require, choose Karechoice as your permanent recruitment partner. We can recruit a wide range of personnel including -\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Registered Nurses</li>\r\n 	<li>Home Managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Unit Managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Registered Managers</li>\r\n 	<li>Directors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe pre-screen responses for your vacancy against the person specification we will have 